I imagine the
people in this room

00:38:01.160 --> 00:38:03.470
are a fairly self-selecting
group, as far

00:38:03.470 --> 00:38:06.980
as being concerned about
these kinds of issues.

00:38:06.980 --> 00:38:10.490
Can you talk about times where,
especially somebody who's

00:38:10.490 --> 00:38:12.740
used to being called intense
in the first meetings

00:38:12.740 --> 00:38:15.954
now for a lot of the reasons
